description:
v2.9.0

This release includes the following changes:

  • Adds ability to assign jobs to technicians, and improves interface for working with jobs.
  • Changes landing page so that technician user sees dashboard of jobs assigned to them.
  • Shows natural language date relative to current time.
  • Improves handling of missing protocol code.

    • Contributions from @marikoja , @gnomicos and @bjkeller
